{"tid":1098253,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"WhatsApp驗證碼騙案升13倍  男子失43萬","createTime":"2019-04-09T02:42:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-09T04:11:53.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"13cdca3f4e94665cecea766c2ffab19924a0ecfd","tid":1098253,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T02:42:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190409/20652097\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190409%2F20652097&d=Srnh2QCYUB68P60bIi3tLdqeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=272711aa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190409%2F20652097&h=e4f576bf\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190409/20652097</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年04月09日 <br />\n<br />\nWhatsApp驗證碼騙案升13倍 <br />\n男子失43萬<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190409/large/0408lai_1008.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190409%2Flarge%2F0408lai_1008.jpg&h=43dc57df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n劉嘉豪提醒市民一旦發現WhatsApp賬戶被騎劫，應立即重新安裝及重新驗證，以「奪回」賬戶。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】WhatsApp驗證碼騙案急升13倍，警方網絡安全及科技罪案調查科署理警司劉嘉豪表示，騙徒入侵目標受害人WhatsApp賬戶，及預先以另一部手機重設受害人的WhatsApp賬戶，並向受害人發出遺失手機、重設賬戶等藉口，要求接收附驗證碼的SMS短訊，一旦受害人回覆，騙徒就可獲取驗證碼，即時騎劫WhatsApp賬號，再以漁翁撒網方式、假扮受害人聯絡親友，要求代購點數卡或現金周轉騙款。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要求買點數卡<br />\n<br />\n警方網絡安全及科技罪案調查科警司曾雅詩指出，這類個案由2017年的42宗飆升至去年的592宗，升幅高達13倍，損失640萬元。今年首季有152宗，比去年同期的227宗下跌33%，但損失金額卻由180萬元增至270萬元，升幅五成；逾九成個案涉騙取點數卡，有47%受害者年齡為41至60歲。<br />\n<br />\n歷來最大宗損失的個案發生於今年1月，一名48歲男子報稱收到「家姐」WhatsApp訊息，要求代購網上遊戲點數卡以供炒賣賺錢，4小時內他先後在屯門黃金海岸寓所附近的便利店購買點數卡逾100次，總值約43萬元。<br />\n<br />\n劉承認至今並無人被捕，指騙徒使用海外伺服器犯案，增警方調查困難，警方正循本地及海外跨境犯案方向調查，提醒市民一旦發現WhatsApp賬戶被騎劫，應立即重新安裝及重新驗證，以「奪回」賬戶，並立即通知親友提防受騙。曾亦提醒市民應為WhatsApp賬戶進行雙步驟驗證防止被盜用，並呼籲便利店職員若發現可疑點數卡交易，應即時查詢及提醒事主。<br />\n<br />\n■記者謝明明  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n懷孕少於12周可致流產<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n蘋人誌：6種身份 2種男人 梁芷珊"},{"pid":"b8f12232ff6ebfa80065653931884f77a4903566","tid":1098253,"uid":164266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T03:28:46.000Z","msg":"幫姐姐買40幾萬點數卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80c732c8cc01ae4227c38a1061f1e4300bedd25e","tid":1098253,"uid":15084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8f12232ff6ebfa80065653931884f77a4903566","tid":1098253,"uid":164266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T03:28:46.000Z","msg":"幫姐姐買40幾萬點數卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T04:01:14.000Z","msg":"點數卡仲有咩用呢個年代？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲停留緊十年前比月費online game"},{"pid":"5c33ccb1d1a18b571cc30f87f5baa282a2210cce","tid":1098253,"uid":54884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T04:02:44.000Z","msg":"姐如果條友冇朋友就昆唔到錢"},{"pid":"385909c778a6c3b76670af5ce765b1547b00c3b0","tid":1098253,"uid":39078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80c732c8cc01ae4227c38a1061f1e4300bedd25e","tid":1098253,"uid":15084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8f12232ff6ebfa80065653931884f77a4903566","tid":1098253,"uid":164266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T03:28:46.000Z","msg":"幫姐姐買40幾萬點數卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T04:01:14.000Z","msg":"點數卡仲有咩用呢個年代？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲停留緊十年前比月費online game"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T04:09:17.000Z","msg":"淘寶啲黑石<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ad76334c10122e871d4e8b4b18adf5fa45f47fa","tid":1098253,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T04:10:45.000Z","msg":"戇鳩"},{"pid":"813edad52a549acb40b32de93270711cd34d6d72","tid":1098253,"uid":116330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T04:11:53.000Z","msg":"其實點數卡除左騙徒工具仲有咩用<br />\n從來冇聽過有其他用途<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不如將便利店收銀機預設一有人買點數卡就自動報警, 追查下落<br />\n相信破到唔少案<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}